{"tid":829423,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)回到未來1-3","createTime":"2018-09-20T12:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T18:24:50.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc9c8b27e3ef2c6cfc634feaca8056d642bc827","tid":829423,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=H03ny1%2BlDNTiShrnUE1SD6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=29dac165\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=H03ny1%2BlDNTiShrnUE1SD6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=bfe58cfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=H03ny1%2BlDNTiShrnUE1SD6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d2de9761\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://ste.india.com/sites/default/files/2015/01/03/309516-back-to-the-future.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fste.india.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F01%2F03%2F309516-back-to-the-future.jpg&h=44c8d741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在1985年的美國，主角馬帝&middot;麥佛萊（Marty McFly），是一個居住在加州山谷市保守家庭裏的17歲高中生，立志成為搖滾巨星。但馬帝的家庭環境並不那麼好：馬帝的父親喬治（George McFly）是個懦弱的小上班族，常受上司畢夫&middot;譚能（Biff Tannen）的刁難；母親羅蘭性格迂腐保守，看不慣任何新生事物。此時，馬帝正計畫著與女友珍妮佛（Jennifer）於週末時開家裡唯一的破車到湖邊露營...........<br />\n<br />\n2.這次，博士和馬蒂說2015年，他的兒子將發生危機，於是他們來到了科技先進的2015年。原來，馬蒂的兒子小馬蒂&middot;麥夫萊（Marty McFly Jr.）在未來即將因為與畢夫的孫子格里夫&middot;譚能（Griff Tannen）惹事生非而遭受牢獄之災，為了避免這一切，博士決定讓馬蒂化裝成小馬蒂的樣子去阻止這一切的發生<br />\n<br />\n3.在第二集的結尾，馬帝依據博士在七十年前留下的信，馬帝和1955年的博士找到了藏在礦穴中的時間機器。馬帝無意間發現在1885年的博士在寄信後不久就將被殺，於是又乘著時間機器趕往1885年。馬帝成功抵達，但油箱卻不慎破損...<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=H03ny1%2BlDNTiShrnUE1SD6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cc0b8c69\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=H03ny1%2BlDNTiShrnUE1SD6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7a32f6d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b6aa7879bcc3bf22e9b74ed3c700ebbb00cb86","tid":829423,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e82ee5c9125b180ca287b09e69db2b98a0312f2","tid":829423,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"還我decade結局"},{"pid":"3939773de53dfdc09e53615b968208cd5aff6c48","tid":829423,"uid":29160,"l